      "description": "$5,900 - Honest poor-condition vehicle best suited for someone looking for a budget project, basic transportation, or parts. It runs and drives, but it shows heavy age and wear throughout and should not be mistaken for a clean or well-kept example. Expect significant cosmetic issues such as faded or damaged paint, body blemishes, visible interior wear, and deferred maintenance. Buyers should plan on repairs, upkeep, and overall reconditioning, so this is being offered as an inexpensive, as-is type vehicle for someone who understands what a rough older used car is.",
