    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Budget-friendly and ready for its next chapter, this vehicle offers an affordable entry point for a handy owner, first-time buyer, or anyone seeking basic transportation at a low cost. It shows clear cosmetic and mechanical wear consistent with age and use, but it still presents an opportunity for the right buyer who values price over perfection. If you\u2019re looking for a practical fixer-upper with strong value potential, this one deserves a look.",
