    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for a budget-friendly ride, starter project, or handy parts car? This one isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s got solid potential for the right buyer and could be a great fit for someone who enjoys bringing a car back to life. Honest old-school value here\u2014priced to move and worth a look if you want something affordable with possibilities.",
      "price": 4800.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 34
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Solid budget-friendly project or daily with a strong-running powertrain and good bones where it counts. The engine pulls cleanly, transmission engages as it should, and it tracks down the road with a confident, planted feel. It shows cosmetic wear and age-related flaws consistent with a well-used vehicle, but it remains a practical, mechanically straightforward car with plenty of life left for the next owner. Great candidate for someone who wants dependable transportation, a weekend fixer, or an affordable platform to sort and improve over time.",
      "price": 6900.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 34
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Cheap driver. Runs, gets you there, priced to sell. Rough around the edges, but hard to beat at this price.",
      "price": 4900.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 34
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "A true diamond-in-the-rough with loads of character, this car has the kind of honest, lived-in presence that turns heads for all the right reasons. It\u2019s the perfect canvas for someone who appreciates a vehicle with soul\u2014whether you\u2019re after a budget-friendly runabout, a weekend project, or something with personality that stands apart from the ordinary. There\u2019s a gritty charm here that hints at stories already told and plenty more waiting to be written. If you\u2019ve got an eye for potential, this one offers an affordable way to get behind the wheel of something memorable.",
      "price": 4950.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 34
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Budget-friendly and full of opportunity, this vehicle is a practical choice for buyers seeking reliable transportation at an accessible price. It shows its age, but it remains a straightforward, honest car that offers real value for someone who wants an inexpensive daily driver, a second vehicle, or a project with potential. Priced to sell and represented transparently, this is a smart way to get behind the wheel without stretching your budget.",
      "price": 4950.0,
